     *           |searchDateTimeEnd     String              通用，搜索日期，双日期的，结束时间【格式：yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss】
     *           |--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     *
     * @return JSON
     * |------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     * |     {
     * |         "resultCode": 0,
     * |         "resultMsg":
     * |         {
     * |                 "recordsFiltered": 25,
